    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Institutions for research, generally part of larger organizations or corporate, industrial, or educational institutions. For independent places where research is conducted, see "research institutes."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
